data.description: Spacious POOL home with BRAND NEW ROOF and HUGE BONUS ROOM in quiet and convenient neighborhood, with NO HOA and NO FLOOD INSURANCE CURRENTLY REQUIRED! This well maintained gem in the heart of St Pete has so much to offer! Your first win is the double corner lot with side facing garage and extra spacious driveway. New fencing on the sides encase the large saltwater pool with covered lanai area, freshly painted deck and screen enclosure. Spacious kitchen features gorgeous solid wood custom cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances (except range), and built in buffet with extra storage and custom slide out features. The huge formal dining room is a real treat and ready for you to create a showcase! Large walk in pantry off the dining room provides plenty of extra storage. This classic home features original hardwood floors in all 3 large bedrooms, and lots of shaded natural light, since all 3 rooms are on exterior corners of the home. Primary bedroom features ensuite bath with walk-in shower, and dual closets. One of the best features of this unique home is the HUGE loft over the garage, with interior stairs access right off the kitchen, fresh paint, newer flooring, recessed lighting, and window unit A/C. This space would be an amazing man cave, teen hangout, studio or workout space, or even a massive 4th bedroom. As if you needed more - there is a large 2 car garage with built-in workbench!! This home truly has it all! Minutes to public transportation, shopping, dining, commuter access, Gandy causeway, and short drive to MacDill and beautiful Florida beaches!! Motivated Seller!
